description: Turn-key West Side 2 bed, 2 bath w/GARAGE parking, 2,500 sqft common roof deck. Highly desirable and rarely available floor plan - foyer entry, open plan living/dining/kitchen with oversized windows flanked on either side with 2 generous bedrooms. Kitchen features gas cooking, granite counters, stylish glass backsplash. Primary suite accommodates king bed + furnishings w/room for additional seating or work area, double wide closet, linen closet, & ensuite w/oversized walk-in shower w/ dual shower heads. 2nd bedroom also fits king & furnishings. Guest bath with deep soaking/jacuzzi tub. 2 common roof decks outfitted with grills, seating areas for dining and relaxing  w/ gorgeous 360* city views. Central Air, laundry on every floor. HVAC, HW & kitchen appliances new in 2022. Prof managed elevator building. Perfectly situated to enjoy all that Southie has to offer - inc PKL Boston, Castle Island Brewing, Tatte, Red Line, beaches, restaurants. Easy access to South End, Seaport & highways.
